org.jivesoftware.smackx.carbons.packet

Class CarbonExtension.Private

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jivesoftware.smackx.carbons.packet.CarbonExtension.Private
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Element, ExtensionElement, NamedElement
    Enclosing class:
    CarbonExtension

    public static class CarbonExtension.Private
extends Object
implements ExtensionElement
    Stanza(/Packet) extension indicating that a message may not be carbon-copied. Adding this extension to any message will disallow that message from being copied.
